      <title>马克韦恩·穆林确认出任国土安全部部长</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/markwayne-mullin-confirmed-homeland-security-secretary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾担任俄克拉荷马州初级参议员的切罗基族成员穆林先生将在关键时刻接任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/markwayne-mullin-confirmed-homeland-security-secretary.html</guid>
