    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉瓜迪亚机场空难造成 2 人死亡，喊“停车”来得太晚</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/nyregion/air-canada-crash-laguardia-nyc.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日晚上，加拿大航空快运的一架喷气式飞机与一辆消防车相撞，造成两名飞行员死亡，数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/nyregion/air-canada-crash-laguardia-nyc.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 02:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆林的顺利确认是参议院的倒退</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/mullins-confirmation-throwback-senate.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统在选择参议员马克韦恩·穆林（Markwayne Mullin）时，是在回归过去的传统。马克韦恩·穆林在国会大厦和政界都有着友好的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/mullins-confirmation-throwback-senate.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 01:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推迟对伊朗的威胁，但战争谈判仍处于早期阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/trump-iran-gas-oil-strait.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统推迟了袭击伊朗发电厂的威胁，称与伊朗人进行了“富有成效的对话”。但官员们表示，谈判还处于早期阶段，并非实质性的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/politics/trump-iran-gas-oil-strait.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 00:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国联邦航空局正在调查另一架喷气式飞机的问题是否分散了拉瓜迪亚空中交通管制员的注意力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/nyregion/faa-air-traffic-controller-laguardia-crash.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，造成两名飞行员死亡的坠机事故发生时，两名管制员正在拉瓜迪亚机场控制中心工作，其中一名管制员正在处理联合航空公司一架飞机上的异味。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/nyregion/faa-air-traffic-controller-laguardia-crash.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 23:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院似乎准备驳回迟到邮寄选票法</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/supreme-court-mail-in-ballots.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数法官似乎对密西西比州的邮寄选票法持怀疑态度，该案可能会颠覆各州处理全国邮寄选票的方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/23/us/supreme-court-mail-in-ballots.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 19:49:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
